<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="as-soon-as">as soon as</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>一...就：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As soon as I hear my alarm clock, I jump out of my bed.
我一听到闹钟响就会跳下床。</p><footer>北师大① – 1</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>如...那么早 / 快：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They didn’t arrive as soon as we had expected.
他们到得没有我们预期的那么早。</p></div></div>